Installation

Clone the repository:
bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/your-username/BookStore.git
Open the index.html file in your preferred web browser.
Usage
Navigate through the website using the provided links in the header and bottom navigation bar.
Explore featured books, categories, deals, and reviews.
Provide feedback through the feedback form.
Features
Responsive design for various screen sizes.
Integration of Swiper.js for slider functionality.
FontAwesome icons for a visually appealing interface.
Sections for featured books, categories, deals, reviews, and feedback.
